Package: headsetcontrol-tray
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, headsetcontrol
Description: System tray widget for HeadsetControl
 A graphical wrapper for headsetcontrol using StatusNotifierItem.
 Supports battery monitoring, sidetone control, and auto power-off.
